data.description: Enjoy affordable and maintenance free living in Knollwood Estates on the Southside of Savannah. This condo is move-in ready. Through the front door there is a half bath and a galley kitchen with an open dining room and living room concept. Enjoy the private fenced patio off the living area! Going up the wood stairs you will find a full bath and a massive bedroom, also with wood floors. The bedroom room beams with natural light from the oversized window and the ensuite walk in closet includes the washer and dryer. All kitchen and laundry appliances are included with the home, as well as access to the community pool. This community is located directly beside St Joseph's Hospital and in close proximity to all Savannah has to offer to include Hunter Army Airfield and Georgia Southern's Armstrong Campus.
